OL,3,C#36.2m football fund 'too Belfast
OL,4,Cfocused'
OL,6,FTwenty football clubs in Northern
OL,7,FIreland are in line for a share of a
OL,8,F#36.2million fund from the Executive
OL,9,Ffor stadium improvement, Communities
OL,10,FMinister Gordon Lyons has announced.
OL,12,FCliftonville and Glentoran are the
OL,13,Flargest clubs which will go through to
OL,14,Fthe next stage of the assessment,
OL,15,Fhaving had bids for works in excess of
OL,16,F#6m progressed.
