OL,6,FHowever, there has been criticism from
OL,7,Fsome politicians that clubs from the
OL,8,Fnorth west area have missed out in the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Football Fund. One
OL,10,FMLA branded the process a "farce".
OL,12,FThe funding was initially announced as
OL,13,Ffar back as 2011 by the Executive.
OL,15,FIn a press conference at H&W Welders
OL,16,FFootball Club in east Belfast, the
OL,17,Fminister announced 20 clubs that will
OL,18,Fprogress to the next stage of the
OL,19,Fprocess.
