OL,6,FMr Lyons said: "These clubs, big and
OL,7,Fsmall, from across Northern Ireland,
OL,8,Fhave impressed with their plans to
OL,9,Fimprove facilities for the game and
OL,10,Ffor local communities."
OL,12,FDepartment for Communities officials
OL,13,Fwill now work with the 20 projects on
OL,14,Fbusiness case development and carry
OL,15,Fout detailed checks.
OL,17,FMr Lyons added: "Together we are
OL,18,Fmoving forward to achieve real change
OL,19,Ffor the benefit of players, fans and
OL,20,Flocal communities. And we are in this
OL,21,Ffor the long haul.
