OL,6,FThe minister announced that
OL,7,FCliftonville and Glentoran were the
OL,8,Ftwo clubs in the running for the tier
OL,9,Fthree grants.
OL,11,FMr Lyons added: "I will be seeking the
OL,12,Ffair and equitable funding which is
OL,13,Fdue after years of delays during which
OL,14,Ftime capital construction costs have
OL,15,Fsoared."
OL,17,FSDLP MLA Mark Durkan queried the
OL,18,Fabsence of clubs from the north west
OL,19,Farea.
