OL,6,FHe said: "There will be bitter
OL,7,Fdisappointment in Derry and across the
OL,8,Fnorth west at the failure to award a
OL,9,Fsingle penny to Derry City Football
OL,10,FClub from the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FFootball Fund.
OL,13,F"Institute FC, who are desperately
OL,14,Fhoping to secure a new home in our
OL,15,Fcity, and Coleraine FC, also in need
OL,16,Fof funding, were excluded ` while most
OL,17,Fof the money was awarded to clubs in
OL,18,Fthe greater Belfast area."
