OL,6,FHe added: "There has been significant
OL,7,Fprogress redeveloping the Brandywell
OL,8,Fin recent years, but we have been
OL,9,Fwaiting nearly 15 years since the Sub
OL,10,FRegional Stadia Programme was first
OL,11,Fannounced, when we were assured Derry
OL,12,FCity would be one of its beneficiaries.
OL,14,F"While the funding was delayed by
OL,15,Fpolitical dysfunction and collapse,
OL,16,Fthe SDLP sought commitments that Derry
OL,17,FCity would be included and were told
OL,18,Frepeatedly by Sinn Fein ministers this
OL,19,Ffunding was 'guaranteed'.
