OL,6,F"To have the rug pulled out at the
OL,7,Flast moment is utterly unacceptable.
OL,8,FTo put it bluntly, this funding
OL,9,Fprocess has been an utter farce from
OL,10,Fstart to finish."
OL,12,FIndependent MLA Claire Sugden said the
OL,13,Ffunding announcement was a "setback"
OL,14,Ffor Coleraine FC.
OL,16,FShe said: "This is not just about
OL,17,Ffacilities for football. Coleraine FC
OL,18,Fis part of the fabric of this
OL,19,Fcommunity. It provides opportunities
OL,20,Ffor young people, supports families,
OL,21,Fand brings people together.
